                            planned and built his 
                                cell  two miles from  Amida  <a href="/815-10" class="factoid-more">See factoid page
                        <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-circle-arrow-right" aria-hidden="true"/></a></p><hr/><p class="indent">Two young men enter the  cell  of Simeon and are
                            unable to leave or put down the food they have taken until Simeon releases them
                            by prayer.  <a href="/815-12" class="factoid-more">See factoid page
                        <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-circle-arrow-right" aria-hidden="true"/></a></p><hr/><p class="indent">Simeon 
                            cooks and lays out food, wine, an inscribed tablet in his  cell  to welcome
                            strangers.  <a href="/815-8" class="factoid-more">See factoid page
                        <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-circle-arrow-right" aria-hidden="true"/></a></p><hr/></div><div class="sources"><h4>Residence: </h4><p class="indent"><span class="tei-persName">Simeon</span> resided in a <span class="tei-placeName"> cell </span> on a
                                mountain two miles from <span class="tei-placeName">
                                    Amida </span>.  <a href="/815-9" class="factoid-more">See factoid page
                        <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-circle-arrow-right" aria-hidden="true"/></a></p></div><div class="citation"><h3>How to cite:</h3><span class="element">
